    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've tried everything. doctors, meds, therapy... nothing touches it. it's just this endless cycle of suffering. sometimes i look at it and i just think, isn't it more merciful to just... stop? like, why is being forced to endure this so much more valued than just finding some peace?",
